<title>CANADA: Viridian to pay Westaim shr dividend.</title>
<headline>Viridian to pay Westaim shr dividend.</headline>
<dateline>FORT SASKATCHEWAN, Alberta 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Viridian Inc said on Friday it will pay a dividend-in-kind of 0.64 of a common share of its subsidiary, the Westaim Corp for each Viridian common share.</p>
</text>
